wordpressPage.title: Pickled Onion Spitting Contest
wordpressPage.content:
Buy a large container of picked onions.  R

oll out  plastic on the floor!

Categorize your crowd by age, grade, gender, whatever
you feel like, and go to it.

Anything from distance, bullseye, goal posts, target, (skies the limit)
and have fun with lots of recognition.
